did.abstract: The materials consist of pictures and photographs of the activities and members of Yale clubs, societies, fraternities, vocal groups, and organizations.

odd.head: General note

processinfo.head: Processing Information
processinfo.p: Yale University records are arranged and described at the accession level by the creating office. The University Archives creates collection level descriptive records, but typically does no further arrangement and description at the accession level.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The materials consist of pictures and photographs of the activities and members of Yale clubs, societies, fraternities, vocal groups, and organizations.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The materials are arranged alphabetically by organization name.
